channel.title: Can any1 help me out, im trying to make a staff list on a empty tab (insidiax)PI
channel.description:
hey guys, i have a insidiax v1 317 PI, and im trying to make a staff list on a tab that is empty , and i have tried doing it but seems like i cannot get it right, when i was trying to do it , i was trying in Client.java, but i didnt find the place that i need to add the codes/scripts too , can anyone give me a step by step guide, as this is my first time doing this im new to it so have no idea about it..
thankyou and please no rude replies or if you cannot help dont just bother posting :) and once again thankyou moparscape,,
